languages.text: "Новой боли? Быть может, тебе удалось предотвратить {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}гибель наших собратьев и Муарана{/d} на Лилэтан? Аребенниан поведал мне обо всем, что случилось".

traits.locale_text: "Новой боли? Быть может, тебе удалось предотвратить гибель наших собратьев и Муарана на мире, что зовется Лилэтан? Почему тыт ак удивлена? Аребенниан поведал мне обо всем, что случилось".

languages.text: "More pain? Did you manage to prevent the {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}death of our kin and Muaran{/d} on the Lilaethan? The Arebennian told me everything that happened."
languages.original_text: "Новой боли? Быть может, тебе удалось предотвратить {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}гибель наших собратьев и Муарана{/d} на Лилэтан? Аребенниан поведал мне обо всем, что случилось".

traits.locale_text: "More pain? Perhaps you managed to prevent the death of our kinsmen and Muaran on Lilaethan? Arebennian told me everything that happened."

languages.text: «¿Más dolor? ¿Acaso evitaste las {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}muertes de los nuestros y de Muaran{/d} en el Lilaethan? El Arebennian me ha relatado todo lo que ocurrió».
languages.original_text: "More pain? Did you manage to prevent the {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}death of our kin and Muaran{/d} on the Lilaethan? The Arebennian told me everything that happened."

traits.locale_text: «¿Más dolor? ¿Acaso evitaste las muertes de los nuestros y de Muaran en Lilaethan? Arebennian me ha contado todo lo que pasó».

languages.text: “更多痛苦？当初在莉莱赞，{d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}我们的族人与穆兰面临死亡{/d}的时候，莫非你救过他们一命吗？独角把那里发生的一切都告诉了我。”
languages.original_text: "More pain? Did you manage to prevent the {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}death of our kin and Muaran{/d} on the Lilaethan? The Arebennian told me everything that happened."

traits.locale_text: “更多痛苦？当初在莉莱赞，我们的族人与穆兰面临死亡的时候，莫非你救过他们一命吗？独角把那里发生的一切都告诉了我。”

languages.text: « Davantage de douleur ? Avez-vous réussi à empêcher {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}la mort de nos semblables et de Muaran{/d} sur la lilaethan ? L'Arebennian m'a tout raconté. »
languages.original_text: "More pain? Did you manage to prevent the {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}death of our kin and Muaran{/d} on the Lilaethan? The Arebennian told me everything that happened."

traits.locale_text: « Davantage de douleur ? Avez-vous réussi à empêcher la mort de nos semblables et de Muaran sur la lilaethan ? Oui, l'arebennian m'a tout raconté. »

languages.text: 「さらなる苦痛？{d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}リラエタンで我らの血族やムアランが死ぬのを{/d}防いだのだろ？アーベニアンから事情は、すべて聞いている」
languages.original_text: "More pain? Did you manage to prevent the {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}death of our kin and Muaran{/d} on the Lilaethan? The Arebennian told me everything that happened."

traits.locale_text: 「さらなる苦痛？リラエタンで我らの血族やムアランが死ぬのを防いだのだろう？アーベニアンから事情は、すべて聞いている」

languages.text: "Noch mehr Schmerz? Vielleicht ist es Euch gelungen, den {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}Tod unserer Brüder und den Muarans{/d} auf der Lileath zu verhindern? Der Arebennian hat mir gesagt, was geschehen ist."
languages.original_text: "More pain? Did you manage to prevent the {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}death of our kin and Muaran{/d} on the Lilaethan? The Arebennian told me everything that happened."

traits.locale_text: "Noch mehr Schmerz? Vielleicht ist es Euch gelungen, den Tod unserer Brüder und den Muarans auf der Lileath zu verhindern? Arebennian hat mir gesagt, was geschehen ist."

languages.text: "Daha fazla acı mı? Lilaethan'da {d|Encyclopedia:Ch2_JanusEldarEliminated}soydaşlarımla Muaran'ın ölümünü{/d} engelleyebildin mi? Arebennian bana olan her şeyi anlattı."
